   [spacer.gif] [spacer.gif] [spacer.gif] Position Statement
   Registered Nurses, under the direction of a Supervising Registered
   Nurse and the Chief Medical Officer in a Youth Authority facility,
   provide direct and indirect nursing care to ward patients.

   [spacer.gif] [spacer.gif] [spacer.gif] Type of Employment
   Variety of Shifts
   Permanent Full-time and
   Permanent Intermittent (on call)

   [spacer.gif] [spacer.gif] [spacer.gif] Locations
   Positions available at youth correctional facilities in the following
   cities;
     * Camarillo
     * Chino
     * Ione
     * Mariposa
     * Nevada City
     * Norwalk
     * Paso Robles
     * Pine Grove
     * Sacramento
     * Santa Cruz
     * Stockton
     * Whittier

