   [spacer.gif] [spacer.gif] [spacer.gif] [spacer.gif] [spacer.gif] How to
   Apply
    1. Obtain a State Application (Form 678) and Supplemental Application,
       you may either download them by clicking on them or contact us to
       have them mailed to you. If you choose to download the application,
       please be advised that you may not be able to save your typed
       application. It is advised that you print each page as you go.
    2. Complete both applications thoroughly. The examination will consist
       of an evaluation of each competitor's experience and education
       using a pre-determined rating criteria. If you need help completing
       the application please download the following instructions;
       Application Instructions
    3. Mail both applications to the above address.

   Note: To be hired, you must possess a current license as a Registered
   Nurse with the State of California.
   [spacer.gif] [spacer.gif] [spacer.gif] Contact Us
   If you have any questions, please feel free call (916) 262-2718 or toll
   free at
   1-866-466-4CYA. You may also E-mail us at cperrin@cya.ca.gov
                                  CYA Seal

   [spacer.gif] [spacer.gif] [spacer.gif] Salary Ranges
   Range A: $3364-4044 per month
   Range B: $3600-4338 per month
   Range A applies to new hires who do not have any nursing experience at
   the time of appointment.
   Range B applies to new hires who have at least one year (or 2080 hours)
   of professional nursing experience at the time of appointment.

   [spacer.gif] [spacer.gif] [spacer.gif] Benefits
     * Paid Annual Leave
     * Medical/Dental Insurance
     * Eligible for Deferred Compensation Retirement Plan, (e.i., 401K)
     * Continuing Education Leave
     * Staff Development Programs....and more.


